== Welcome to Finanze

This is a simple Rails application to manage your daily expenses. 

Features included:
- monthly view of your expenses
- filter your expenses by category with tag cloud
- google charts for monthly reports
- current month total expense prevision
- left for this month based on your wage

Todo list:

- Move wage configuration from environment to yml file
- Complete translating views to HAML
- Introduce Rails.logger instead of puts where required
